name: Disney Sing It! - High School Musical 3: Senior Year
name_original: Disney Sing It! - High School Musical 3: Senior Year
description:
Disney Sing It! - High School Musical 3: Senior Year is an arcade game developed by Zoë Mode. It came out on 28-11-2008. Disney Interactive published the game.
Disney Sing It! - High School Musical 3: Senior Year is available on PC, PlayStation 2 and PlayStation 3.
